<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-asset-resolution-limited> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "UK Asset Resolution Limited (UKAR) is responsible for meeting the contractual obligations and managing the remaining liabilities and other strategic matters arising out of the Government’s former ownership of NRAM Ltd (NRAM), Bradford & Bingley (B&B), Mortgage Express (MX) and their respective subsidiaries. UKAR works with HM Treasury and the UK Government Investments ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
